cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.HC 

This paper discusses the optimization of cyber hygiene measures for protecting healthcare users, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also utilizes game theory and combinatorial optimization, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). Additionally, the focus on healthcare users suggests a potential connection to healthcare informatics (cs.HC) and the consideration of indirect costs could relate to social and information networks (cs.SI).
